******************** optimal app **************************

1 use post order dfs 
2 for every node recursively from bottom (while recursion is returning) check its leftsum + rightsum equals root data or not 
4 if value is not equal return false by skipping other recursive calls 
5 otherwise return leftsum + rightsum + rootdata to uppper node 

